  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                        Save the Universe with your movement!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will need to be agile and precise, but don't worry... you've got this.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid enemies and Somber Slumber at all costs! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can find up to 350 pieces of scattered Dough and 105 planetoids in your quest to discover outer space's every nook and cranny. Other secrets also await.<br>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/0a7a89d0bc023502b3ce9a5dcb3ed214.poster.avif?t=1746468651\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/0a7a89d0bc023502b3ce9a5dcb3ed214.webm?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/0a7a89d0bc023502b3ce9a5dcb3ed214.mp4?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alongside hypnotic pixel art graphics and a dazzlingly atmospheric soundtrack, BeDo offers an immersive, fun and challenging experience.     </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It's both accessible and tough. Everyone can start and progress in the adventure, but exploring every corner of the universe won't be an easy task. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax gliding across mysterious galaxies… or dashing quickly to the golden goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/3911cd400d5bde274727f6873e2c9dc1.poster.avif?t=1746468651\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/3911cd400d5bde274727f6873e2c9dc1.webm?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/3911cd400d5bde274727f6873e2c9dc1.mp4?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><i>BeDo is a unique game, difficult to classify —and it feels refreshingly simple at its core: move a mysterious dough through the universe. How well can you control your spatial slides? Can you lead BeDo to the goal in every level?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/588a4e6a9185a90e24bc46b84a3f2a01.poster.avif?t=1746468651\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/588a4e6a9185a90e24bc46b84a3f2a01.webm?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/588a4e6a9185a90e24bc46b84a3f2a01.mp4?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                                Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control BeDo in full precision: lead him in all directions as you float through space </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 40 handcrafted colorful levels teeming with collectibles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge Evil: Skill and precision are paramount to sort and avoid obstacles, enemies and traps in your path </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Dough of Vital Creation that was scattered throughout the Universe </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secret areas and unlock valuable secrets </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A galactic, nostalgic and intriguing soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                        Save the Universe with your movement!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will need to be agile and precise, but don't worry... you've got this.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid enemies and Somber Slumber at all costs! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can find up to 350 pieces of scattered Dough and 105 planetoids in your quest to discover outer space's every nook and cranny. Other secrets also await.<br>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/0a7a89d0bc023502b3ce9a5dcb3ed214.poster.avif?t=1746468651\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/0a7a89d0bc023502b3ce9a5dcb3ed214.webm?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/0a7a89d0bc023502b3ce9a5dcb3ed214.mp4?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alongside hypnotic pixel art graphics and a dazzlingly atmospheric soundtrack, BeDo offers an immersive, fun and challenging experience.     </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > It's both accessible and tough. Everyone can start and progress in the adventure, but exploring every corner of the universe won't be an easy task. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax gliding across mysterious galaxies… or dashing quickly to the golden goal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/3911cd400d5bde274727f6873e2c9dc1.poster.avif?t=1746468651\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/3911cd400d5bde274727f6873e2c9dc1.webm?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/3911cd400d5bde274727f6873e2c9dc1.mp4?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><i>BeDo is a unique game, difficult to classify —and it feels refreshingly simple at its core: move a mysterious dough through the universe. How well can you control your spatial slides? Can you lead BeDo to the goal in every level?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/588a4e6a9185a90e24bc46b84a3f2a01.poster.avif?t=1746468651\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/588a4e6a9185a90e24bc46b84a3f2a01.webm?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2325340/extras/588a4e6a9185a90e24bc46b84a3f2a01.mp4?t=1746468651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                                Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control BeDo in full precision: lead him in all directions as you float through space </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 40 handcrafted colorful levels teeming with collectibles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge Evil: Skill and precision are paramount to sort and avoid obstacles, enemies and traps in your path </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Dough of Vital Creation that was scattered throughout the Universe </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secret areas and unlock valuable secrets </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A galactic, nostalgic and intriguing soundtrack</p></li></ul>",
